commissionName: NSLOCTEXT("", "9CB8CAA745132B3E92B979B65E7E47B5", "Bounty: Cursed By the Final Command")
flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "90AED63A46F361B91EAA848E879E889E", "Seek and slay the Echo of Command. Ancient records speak of a mad warlord who led his knights to hunt a peaceful giant. At Titan\'s Ring, they cornered the giant, who begged for mercy and offered allegiance, but the warlord\'s final command sealed its fate. The giant\'s blood awakened the ring\'s power, and a curse fell upon the warlord and his knights, binding them to guard the site of their treachery for eternity. The curse endures, fueled by that final, merciless command. -The Striders Vigilant")
